data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath concrete block home on .34 acre. Home was remodeled in 2022. New bathrooms, new LVP flooring throughout entire home, knock down ceilings, New electric garage door opener, new lighting fixtures, new door hardware, etc. Beautiful kitchen, stainless steel appliances, high end soft close wood cabinets with high end knobs. Home also includes, fresh paint inside and out, a new concrete driveway/walkway with a beautiful new tiled front porch. Large Owner's bedroom w/ Owner's bathroom and walk-in closet. Other Notable Features: Roof 2017, Water heater 2021, HVAC 2022, Electric Panel 2022, Concrete driveway/walkway 2022. Home can be sold furnished as shown with acceptable offer.
